Text: Thanks!! But how do i add the subtitles too the movie??
Hey Quick Question, What Are leechers? ,,Newie here,,
And Thank you Very Much For The Up. Much Appreciated!

@ Midnight_Lady
A Google search might give you the quickest, most in depth answer for your question. But simply put, leechers are taking the parts of a given file from whoever can provide it (seeders). So, seeders have the file and provide it to leechers who do not yet have the file and are downloading it.
